snippet.title: The Silver Lining Of A Trump Nomination

localized.description:
On the upside of Donald Trump victory on the Republican side, all of the things corporate pundits have been telling us about conservative voters weren't true. You don't have to be pro-megabanks, hyper-religious, or a thousand percent on Israel's side all the time. Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola (ThinkTank), and Jimmy Dore, hosts of The Young Turks, break it down. Tell us what you think in the comment section below.

Hosts: Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore

Cast: Cenk Uygur, Ana Kasparian, John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore
